author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Graphic Signs Preliminary Agreement On Acquisition Of Property In Gdynia
text:
Feb 22 (Reuters) - GRAPHIC SA:
* SAID ON WEDNESDAY THAT IT SIGNED PRELIMINARY AGREEMENT ON ACQUISITION OF PROPERTY IN GDYNIA FOR 750,000 ZLOTYS
* ON ABOVE-MENTIONED PROPERTY COMPANY INTENDS TO EXECUTE MULTI-FAMILY HOUSING PROJECT
